For me, photography is the art, science, and practice of creating pictures by recording radiation on a radiation-sensitive medium, such as a photographic film, or electronic image sensors. I don't mind my pict didn't go to the popular page as long as I enjoy my editing and being satisfy with the result. It's my day 2 joining the #gang_family and my month 7th joining the #iphonesia family. Both of this groups are incredible and awesome... All the members are "talented" and always learning and sharing. Some are very nice people who's really know how to create a fascinating and catching the eye picture using their iPhone, iPod, iPad or DSLR. Thanks for accepting me for the friendship and for the love of photography and NOT for the sake of being POPULAR!!! Popular is a BONUS, but what I really admire you is your love of photography. Please apologize if I have to remove or unfollow some of you (again or new). Thanks for the friendship all... Love ya... #rervin #iphonesia #gang_family #hdr
